      "description": "Reliable transportation at a budget-friendly price. This vehicle is being offered as an affordable option for buyers who want practical value and a straightforward driving experience. It shows its age and would best suit someone comfortable with an older used vehicle, but it remains a compelling opportunity for inexpensive ownership. Priced to sell and worth a look for the right buyer.",
