      "description": "Honest little project car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it starts, moves, and could be a great budget runabout, parts car, or weekend fixer-upper. If you\u2019re handy with cars or just want something affordable with potential, this could be a solid opportunity. Priced to sell and ready for someone to give it a new chapter.",
