    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast upside. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels composed, and it has the kind of analog, mechanical character that\u2019s getting harder to find. Cosmetically it shows its age and it\u2019s not a showroom car, but for someone who wants an affordable entry point with good bones, this is a compelling platform to drive as-is, sort further, or build into something special. Priced for a quick sale and worth a look if you appreciate a car with real character.",
